10. Wang L, Stuber T, Camp P, et al. Whole-genome sequencing of porcine epidemic diarrhea virus by Illumina MiSeq Platform. In: Wang L, editor. Animal coronaviruses. Totowa (NJ): Humana Press; 2016. p. 201-8.

